			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Meet the Killer Whales You Thought You Knew</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">The iconic marine mammals may not belong to one species but several. Surprise!</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/craig-welch/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Craig Welch</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
