						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AMeet the Killer Whales You Thought You Knew%0D%0AThe iconic marine mammals may not belong to one species but several. Surprise!%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/features/meet-the-killer-whales-you-thought-you-knew/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



